import { Box, Typography, Link, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import InstagramIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Instagram';
import WhatsAppIcon from '@mui/icons-material/WhatsApp';

const Footer = () => (
  <Box
    component="footer"
    sx={{
      background: '#566542',
      color: '#fff',
      py: 4,
      px: 2,
      mt: 8,
      textAlign: 'center',
    }}
  >
    <Typography variant="subtitle1" sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
      Psicólogo Cristian Hendler  |  CRP 07/42111
    </Typography>
    <Box sx={{ mt: 1, mb: 2 }}>
      <Link href="#home" color="#e9e6e1" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Início</Link>
      <Link href="#about" color="#e9e6e1" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Sobre</Link>
      <Link href="#services" color="#e9e6e1" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Serviços</Link>
      <Link href="#contact" color="#e9e6e1" underline="hover" sx={{ mx: 1, fontWeight: 500 }}>Contato</Link>
    </Box>
    <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
      <IconButton
        href="https://www.instagram.com/psicocrishendler/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        sx={{ color: '#e9e6e1', mx: 1, '&:hover': { color: '#7a5430' } }}
        aria-label="Instagram"
      >
        <InstagramIcon />
      </IconButton>
      <IconButton
        href="https://wa.me/5551996024420"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        sx={{ color: '#e9e6e1', mx: 1, '&:hover': { color: '#7a5430' } }}
        aria-label="WhatsApp"
      >
        <WhatsAppIcon />
      </IconButton>
    </Box>
    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#e9e6e1', opacity: 0.8 }}>
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} Cristian Hendler. Todos os direitos reservados.
    </Typography>
  </Box>
);

export default Footer;
